'''Seoulian''' was the [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Seoularian]]s, a [[Human/Legends|Human]] people resistant to [[Force power/Legends|Force powers]] that controlled an area of [[Realspace/Legends|space]] from their [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]], [[Seoul 5]]. They were wiped out in a cosmic war eons before the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], though some of their inscriptions survived.

